  "body": "I can send messages as another user that I have no relation to (not mutual contacts, never initiated DM). This is not simply a graphical glitch, as it shows up as the other user sent it on all versions of mobile and desktop clients.\r\n\r\nTo reproduce: tap send button while shaking phone to attempt a bug report. If you time it right, the bug report action is never shown, and the message is sent by whoever sent the previous one. Must be on mobile data.\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65834069/204108573-ac6163d9-236f-4356-a887-da53e1f18e30.mp4\r\n\r\n",
